Add experimental support for [MSC4350](https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-spec-proposals/pull/4350) (encryption impersonation for appservices), behind the `experimental_features.msc4350_enabled` config flag. With the flag enabled, `/keys/upload` accepts the unstable `fi.mau.msc4350.impersonator` field on device-keys entries and validates the spec invariants (empty `algorithms`/`keys`, well-formed impersonator object, signature-entry presence). Cryptographic signature verification and `/keys/query` response augmentation will land in follow-up commits.
